participants.name: Bridget Sharpe
participants.title: Government Affairs and Industry Relations Manager at Professional Beauty Association

messages.message: Gary is the chairman of the AZ state board of cosmetology. I work for the professional beauty association in government affairs so we work with the state boards pretty regularly.
You just became the second most important person in my life.  Iga is apply for his school.  She has had a passion for this for over 18 years.  I have a passion for policy.  I miss you!
I have an interview for "Arizona State" tomorrow.  Not sure what that means, some recruiter is trying to pimp me out.  Pretty excited about the proximity though.
City council is a huge waste of time.
Aren't you so excited about the winner of America?  :D
Are you excited about your move to the new office coming up in June?
I thought they were moving all the government offices downtown?
Oh that makes sense.  Iga signed up for school at IMAj.  Starts in December.
